{
  "id": "RAW_c91bb2",
  "title": "一张照片实现超 70 种百万级运镜！这款 AI 神器给了摄影师一记「铁拳」 ｜ 机器之心",
  "url": "https://www.jiqizhixin.com/articles/2025-05-12-15",
  "date": "2025-05-12 09:45:00",
  "author": "AI好好用",
  "siteName": "机器之心",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/71ee82e2-ab9f-4ba8-4a2b-ef4287df1400/public\" alt=\"image.png\" data-ratio=\"0.5564814814814815\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-imgfileid=\"100044668\" data-original-style=\"null\" data-index=\"1\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/b991cbf9-c50c-426a-a8d2-90b99fe94cdf/640.png\" data-report-img-idx=\"0\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 700%;\"></p>\n  <p><strong data-immersive-translate-walked=\"4d382231-b98e-4570-bcea-526c44b96c5c\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span data-immersive-translate-walked=\"4d382231-b98e-4570-bcea-526c44b96c5c\">编辑&nbsp;</span>|<span data-immersive-translate-walked=\"4d382231-b98e-4570-bcea-526c44b96c5c\">&nbsp;杨文</span></strong></p>\n  <p>去年 9 月份，我们盘点了 100% AI 生成的各种广告大片。不过彼时的 AI 广告镜头还有着不少瑕疵，比如稍显奇怪的手指：</p>\n  <p><img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/f8bc0e3d-3ba3-4921-ff1c-71b2ea875000/public\" alt=\"image.png\" data-ratio=\"0.7657407407407407\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"430\" data-imgfileid=\"100044628\" data-original-style=\"width: 100%;\" data-index=\"2\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/70195b1e-48e9-4ac6-9c85-63d452a22be0/640.png\" data-report-img-idx=\"1\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 700%;\"></p>\n  <p>模特行走时快要崴断的脚脖子：</p>\n  <p><img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/cc068471-c3bb-4563-ce9e-fba56050b800/public\" alt=\"image.png\" data-ratio=\"0.774074074074074\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-imgfileid=\"100044629\" data-original-style=\"null\" data-index=\"3\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/8d8bfdf5-a3d3-489a-95b7-f4e1e41c3fff/640.png\" data-report-img-idx=\"2\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 700%;\"></p>\n  <p>经过半年的进化，AI 视频技术已然进入到下一个阶段。</p>\n  <p>前不久，音乐组合 Partyof2 花了 2500 美元拍了个视频。</p>\n  <p><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/9_vre_W7vYsyKgNtB7puhQ\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/ab5b2f5a-4d59-45ce-a73e-76c57fd42022/1747042955347.png\" style=\"width: 700%;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\"></a>有博主利用一款名为 Higgsfield 的 AI 视频生成工具，一比一复刻了这些镜头，效果不说一模一样，只能说是毫无区别。</p>\n  <p>据博主介绍，只需上传一张歌手的图像，选择 Higgsfield AI 的「Mouth In」（嘴部特写）镜头运动功能，几分钟内就能生成上面这个专业级镜头。</p>\n  <section>\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/145f9606-ea42-41a8-9e4c-a46d972b8600/public\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"640\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"325\" data-imgfileid=\"100044638\" data-original-style=\"width: 100%;\" data-index=\"4\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/5e7744a8-2865-4d79-9ecb-77ad87cfeece/640.gif\" data-order=\"0\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"8\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 700%;\">\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/8ed7e283-2e9e-4a31-6cd5-f92222b8f800/public\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"640\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"325\" data-imgfileid=\"100044637\" data-original-style=\"width: 100%;\" data-index=\"5\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/341d58fd-8584-4f12-9bf8-7f076a257af4/640.gif\" data-order=\"1\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"4\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 700%;\">\n  </section>\n  <p>下面这个镜头则用到了 Higgsfield AI 的另一项惊人特效 ——「机械臂运镜（ROBO ARM）」，Higgsfield 是目前唯一能实现此类高难度动态运镜 AI 模型。</p>\n  <section>\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/43da768a-098d-4e8d-6ca9-fe59f17e7a00/public\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"640\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"325\" data-imgfileid=\"100044636\" data-original-style=\"width: 100%;\" data-index=\"6\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/2313be3a-8071-47c2-ab0c-81d6d226b01c/640.gif\" data-order=\"2\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"9\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 700%;\">\n  </section>\n  <p>X 博主「Angry Tom」则用 Higgsfield 制作了一个可口可乐的广告大片。</p>\n  <p>别看视频中有着大量复杂的运镜效果，其实它只花了 9 美元，用了 47 分钟。</p>\n  <p><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/9_vre_W7vYsyKgNtB7puhQ\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/5bd04226-a86e-4a8e-ab5b-489e04fa5583/1747042988027.png\" style=\"width: 700%;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\"></a></p>\n  <p>-1-</p>\n  <p>超 70 种运镜</p>\n  <p>Higgsfield AI 由前 Snap 公司高管 Alex Mashrabov 创立，旨在通过预设运镜模板和高度自定义功能，帮助用户轻松制作电影级动态视频。</p>\n  <p>目前，Higgsfield 提供超过 70 种预设运镜模板，如 360 度环绕拍摄（360 Orbit）、子弹时间（Bullet Time）、动作奔跑镜头（Action Run） 等。</p>\n  <p><img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/37f235a1-a2ca-4321-df3f-85e4305f3d00/public\" alt=\"image.png\" data-ratio=\"0.4305555555555556\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-imgfileid=\"100044643\" data-original-style=\"null\" data-index=\"7\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/1abe73c6-25ec-4e2a-bbd1-dff5a96ef087/640.png\" data-report-img-idx=\"3\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 700%;\"></p>\n  <p>接下来，我们挑几个不错的运镜效果来展开一下。</p>\n  <p>1.Focus Change（焦点转换）</p>\n  <p>在同一个镜头中将焦点从一个主体转移到另一个主体，引导观众的注意力，非常适合用于叙事、揭示情节或强调情感。</p>\n  <p>提示词：Focus on the man who looked towards the girl. Focus shifts to the girl who walks straight to the camera and looks at it confidently and poses.（聚焦于看向女孩的男人，镜头焦点随后转移到女孩身上，她径直走向镜头，并自信地看向镜头并摆出姿势。）</p>\n  <section>\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/9d752642-cccd-4b6b-91ba-6499b44b0e00/public\" data-ratio=\"1.3333333333333333\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"600\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100044644\" data-original-style=\"null\" data-index=\"8\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/ca214e28-19d9-4ed0-b457-2d8fe478fd13/640.gif\" data-order=\"3\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"17\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 700%;\">\n  </section>\n  <p>2.Fisheye （鱼眼）</p>\n  <p>这是一种宽广且扭曲的镜头效果，使画面边缘弯曲，让一切看起来圆润且夸张，为镜头增添了一种有趣、超现实或前卫的氛围。</p>\n  <p>提示词：A man dances energetically, showcasing stylish movements with confidence. He is dressed in oversized, flowing pants and a sleek black jacket, embodying an urban vibe. The scene is set in a dimly lit underground tunnel, bathed in vibrant green light that gleams off the concrete walls. The fisheye lens distorts the surroundings, exaggerating the dancer's dynamic poses as they seem to leap into the lens. A palpable sense of energy fills the atmosphere, with each movement reflecting a fusion of rhythm and emotion. The stark contrast of the green light against the darkened space amplifies his presence, creating a hypnotic effect that invites the viewer into his world.（一名男子充满活力地跳舞，自信地展示出时尚的动作。他穿着宽松飘逸的裤子和一件光滑的黑色夹克，展现出一种都市风格。场景设定在一个昏暗的地下隧道中，整个空间被明亮的绿色光线笼罩，光线在混凝土墙壁上闪闪发光。鱼眼镜头扭曲了周围的环境，夸张了舞者的动态姿势，仿佛他正跃入镜头之中。整个氛围充满了强烈的能量，每一个动作都体现了节奏与情感的融合。绿色光线与黑暗空间的鲜明对比，突显了他的存在，营造出一种催眠效果，将观众引入他的世界。）</p>\n  <section>\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/8772604d-9438-4449-0fff-db9bea0a5200/public\" data-ratio=\"1\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"600\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"578\" data-imgfileid=\"100044652\" data-original-style=\"width: 100%;\" data-index=\"9\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/76449c8a-5271-4045-8cc1-f2df505e3ab6/640.gif\" data-order=\"4\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"10\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 700%;\">\n  </section>\n  <p>3.Whip Pan （快速摇摄）</p>\n  <p>一种快速的镜头平移，使画面变得模糊，用于镜头之间的过渡或增加能量和速度感，非常适合用于动作场景、喜剧或突然的场景切换。</p>\n  <p>提示词：The scene begins with a tense standoff — a group of soldiers in striped uniforms, standing in formation. The camera hovers uncomfortably close to the rigid backs of the armed men. The air is heavy, silent.Suddenly, with a sharp whip pan, the camera snaps to the side — fast motion blurs the screen before landing on a lone detective. He stands apart, leaning against a wooden post. He’s clad in a wrinkled beige trench coat, fedora tipped low, shielding his tired eyes. A thin trail of smoke curls upward from the cigarette clutched between his fingers. His gaze is fixed on the soldiers, but his expression is calm.（场景开始于一场紧张的对峙 —— 一群穿着条纹制服的士兵，排成队列站着。镜头不自然地贴近那些武装士兵僵硬的后背，空气凝重，寂静无声。突然，随着一个快速的甩镜头，镜头猛地转向一侧 —— 快速移动使画面模糊，随后定格在一个孤独的侦探身上。他独自站着，倚靠在一根木柱上。他穿着一件起皱的米色风衣，头戴一顶压得很低的软呢帽，遮住了他疲惫的眼睛。他手指间夹着的香烟上方飘起一缕细烟，他的目光盯着那些士兵，但他的表情却很平静。）</p>\n  <section>\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/65615406-b53d-49a5-dd82-95d60ae3af00/public\" data-ratio=\"0.5633333333333334\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"600\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100044655\" data-original-style=\"null\" data-index=\"10\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/480b810e-3fc9-46f9-8716-5dd1aed90366/640.gif\" data-order=\"5\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"14\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 700%;\">\n  </section>\n  <p>4.Robo Arm （机械臂）</p>\n  <p>使用高速机器人摄像机进行快速、精准且富有电影感的运动拍摄，非常适合用于流畅的运动镜头、产品展示或动态过渡效果。</p>\n  <p>提示词：A man in a business suit stands in a sterile office environment, his face reflecting confusion or unease. The white walls, sharp lines, and bright lighting give the space an air of strict order and control. A badge hangs from his neck, reinforcing the corporate setting. His posture and expression hint at an underlying tension within this meticulously structured world.（一位穿着商务西装的男子站在一个毫无生气的办公室环境中，他的脸上流露出困惑或不安的神情。白色的墙壁、锐利的线条和明亮的灯光让这个空间显得秩序井然、严格受控。他的脖子上挂着一个徽章，进一步强化了这种企业化的氛围。他的姿态和表情暗示着，在这个精心构建的世界里，他内心深处存在着某种紧张感。）</p>\n  <section>\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/f5d90685-c605-4b1f-6441-96883a92e300/public\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"640\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"325\" data-imgfileid=\"100044651\" data-original-style=\"width: 100%;\" data-index=\"11\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/aa031383-ff2a-43ce-a27d-7494ed8758e0/640.gif\" data-order=\"6\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"11\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 700%;\">\n  </section>\n  <p>此外，Higgsfield 还推出了 Mix 混合运镜功能，支持多种镜头动态组合，突破传统物理限制，实现现实中无法完成的镜头语言。</p>\n  <p>Crane Over The Head x Crash Zoom In&nbsp;</p>\n  <p>（头顶越肩 + 撞击式推近）</p>\n  <p>以平滑的俯瞰上升开始，然后突然推近主体，带来戏剧性的冲击力，结合了宏大渐进的气势与强烈的聚焦瞬间。</p>\n  <p>提示词：The camera zooms in on her head, capturing the shimmering, oversized sunglasses reflecting the vivid colors of a neon-lit room. She exudes confidence, her braided hair cascading down her shoulder as she forms a peace sign with one hand. The ambient glow of red and blue illuminates her metallic silver puffer jacket, blending seamlessly with the electric motifs on the walls. The environment feels alive, pulsating with energy as the dynamic lighting shifts, enhancing her striking presence. Her bold expression conveys a sense of defiance and individuality, inviting viewers into this electrifying world.（镜头推近她的头部，捕捉到她那闪亮的超大号太阳镜反射出霓虹灯房间的鲜艳色彩。她散发着自信，一头编成辫子的头发垂落在肩上，她用一只手比出一个和平手势。周围弥漫的红光和蓝光照亮了她那件金属银色的羽绒服，与墙上的电子图案无缝融合。整个环境充满了生机，随着动态灯光的变换而脉动，增强了她引人注目的存在感。她大胆的表情传达出一种反抗和个性，邀请观众进入这个充满活力的世界。）</p>\n  <section>\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/653e3a0b-3115-415f-7bf6-52f15a890800/public\" data-ratio=\"0.6583333333333333\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"600\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100044645\" data-original-style=\"null\" data-index=\"12\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/73dcee04-fbf4-49c1-91c5-012f7ca0d3f8/640.gif\" data-order=\"7\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"22\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 700%;\">\n  </section>\n  <p>-2-</p>\n  <p>一手实测</p>\n  <p>Higgsfield 的玩法非常简单，只需选择一种运镜模版，比如「360 Orbit」（360 度环绕）运镜，再上传一张人物照片。</p>\n  <p><img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/28940352-0cab-4a87-6df2-482c5c327600/public\" alt=\"image.png\" data-ratio=\"0.48333333333333334\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-imgfileid=\"100044656\" data-original-style=\"null\" data-index=\"13\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/4a4580f9-5e5a-40e3-91ec-0a76a08267dd/640.png\" data-report-img-idx=\"5\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 700%;\"></p>\n  <p>静待几分钟即可生成具有复杂摄像机运动效果的视频。</p>\n  <p>视频中确实呈现出 360 环绕运镜效果，但女生扭头的动作幅度过大，显得非常诡异。</p>\n  <p><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/9_vre_W7vYsyKgNtB7puhQ\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/0e148a9b-924d-4b9b-a813-628acf256b16/1747043040730.png\" style=\"width: 700%;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\"></a></p>\n  <section>\n   <span data-cover=\"http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FDT8udUick9sK2iazHFLM87Sd1fjB7Z6wKVicag6VWUlMwncq7bFjfqXEIZ0mztxB2QvQFEAF5eOr6zMtWCxTdXPZg%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\" data-mpvid=\"wxv_3963449075508133893\" data-ratio=\"0.55\" data-src=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/mp/readtemplate?t=pages/video_player_tmpl&amp;auto=0&amp;vid=wxv_3963449075508133893\" data-vh=\"492.9375\" data-vidtype=\"2\" data-vw=\"657.25\" data-w=\"704\" height=\"508\" scrolling=\"no\" width=\"661\"></span>它还可以调整镜头速度、角度、灯光等参数，结合 AI 提示词增强工具，自动优化画面描述以增强动态效果。例如，输入中文提示词后，系统会转化为专业英文指令并补充动作细节。\n  </section>\n  <p>同时，它还支持与 GPT-4o 等图像生成工具结合，先制作高质量图片再转化为动态视频。</p>\n  <p>我们先使用它的文生图功能，生成一张梅西和 C 罗的自拍照。</p>\n  <p>输入的提示词：请你生成张极其平凡无奇的自拍照，没有明确的主体或者构图感，就是随手一拍的快照，照片略带运动模糊，阳光或室内打光不均导致的轻微曝光过度，整体呈现出一种刻意的平庸感，就像是不小心拍到的一张自拍，主角是守望先锋里的 C 罗，旁边是梅西。</p>\n  <p><img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/74a6b6ff-341a-4121-14a4-8563cfd0d000/public\" alt=\"image.png\" data-ratio=\"1\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1024\" data-imgfileid=\"100044665\" data-original-style=\"null\" data-index=\"14\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/153f71d2-8a67-4e56-924f-9ac805a4f9c5/640.png\" data-report-img-idx=\"6\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 700%;\"></p>\n  <p>然后使用 Mix 混合运镜功能，将「头顶越肩 + 撞击式推近」镜头组合在一起：</p>\n  <section>\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/4190a276-47c8-45e6-ef82-6a0f4ed82400/public\" data-ratio=\"1\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"540\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"540\" data-backh=\"540\" data-imgfileid=\"100044823\" data-original-style=\"width: 100%;\" data-index=\"15\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/97e5a93a-a781-494b-bfe3-688f91ee5308/640.gif\" data-order=\"8\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"18\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 700%;\">\n  </section>\n  <p>此外，Higgsfield 最近还上新了 7 种新运镜，分别是 <span data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">Face Punch、Arc Left 、Arc Right 、Jib Up 、Jib Down 、Double Dolly 、Static。</span></p>\n  <p>Face Punch （面部重击）</p>\n  <p>捕捉到面部被重拳击中的瞬间，强烈而充满原始能量，非常适合用于动作场景、打斗场景或紧张的特写镜头。</p>\n  <section>\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/d9306cc8-cf07-48e1-8a9e-8d5f35504100/public\" data-ratio=\"0.7537037037037037\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"540\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"540\" data-backh=\"407\" data-imgfileid=\"100044650\" data-original-style=\"width: 100%;\" data-index=\"16\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/c16669fe-f330-4e91-b7ff-27facb0bb9e9/640.gif\" data-order=\"9\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"12\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 700%;\">\n  </section>\n  <p>Arc Left（向左弧形移动）</p>\n  <p>镜头优雅地向左围绕主体弧形移动，增加了运动感、焦点感和电影风格，非常适合用于情感的积累或视觉效果的提升。</p>\n  <section>\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/2fe8ad0a-0018-42a0-5683-9f0f677efb00/public\" data-ratio=\"1.326\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"500\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"500\" data-backh=\"663\" data-imgfileid=\"100044646\" data-original-style=\"width:100%;\" data-index=\"17\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/25312286-8eea-4908-8f07-034d463022b2/640.gif\" data-order=\"10\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"21\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 700%;\">\n  </section>\n  <p>Arc Right（向右弧形移动）</p>\n  <p>镜头围绕主体平稳地沿弧线向右移动，增加了画面的深度和戏剧性。非常适合用于需要电影感的浪漫、史诗或紧张场景。</p>\n  <section>\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/c273b11a-4c35-45a6-f8af-8edf3ed51800/public\" data-ratio=\"1\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"540\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"540\" data-backh=\"540\" data-imgfileid=\"100044647\" data-original-style=\"width: 100%;\" data-index=\"18\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/cca0c18d-a8c3-4037-a093-3d94ca691bcf/640.gif\" data-order=\"11\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"19\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 700%;\">\n  </section>\n  <p>Jib Up（摇臂上升）</p>\n  <p>镜头沿着垂直方向平稳上升，展示出更多场景内容或强调高度，非常适合用于宏大开场或场景过渡。</p>\n  <p><img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/632cd27d-c81d-4ec0-c849-2133d8222e00/public\" data-ratio=\"0.7533333333333333\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"600\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100044654\" data-original-style=\"null\" data-index=\"19\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/332db8fd-bcf6-442d-818e-3ede68557938/640.gif\" data-order=\"12\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"15\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 700%;\"></p>\n  <p>Jib Down（摇臂下降）</p>\n  <p>镜头轻轻向下移动，聚焦于主体或揭示下方的内容，非常适合用于戏剧性的登场或场景的展开。</p>\n  <section>\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/026beee4-0a5c-4ea9-5b76-5f7364c3a800/public\" data-ratio=\"0.6583333333333333\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"600\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"381\" data-imgfileid=\"100044653\" data-original-style=\"width: 100%;\" data-index=\"20\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/d34aab1f-5df1-4c2b-a320-c9ba42cf4949/640.gif\" data-order=\"13\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"20\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 700%;\">\n  </section>\n  <p>Double Dolly（双重平移）</p>\n  <p>镜头和主体同时在平移车上移动，使主体在画面中保持完全静止，而背景则发生变化。这种拍摄方式能够创造出超现实的漂浮效果，常用于音乐视频和梦幻场景中。</p>\n  <section>\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/6b7abca8-3a6b-4166-535a-187fd5118400/public\" data-ratio=\"0.5703703703703704\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"540\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"540\" data-backh=\"308\" data-imgfileid=\"100044648\" data-original-style=\"width: 100%;\" data-index=\"21\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/3148ed4e-1426-469e-a183-a03ceda185dc/640.gif\" data-order=\"14\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"16\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 700%;\">\n  </section>\n  <p>Static 静态</p>\n  <p>镜头完全静止，没有任何移动或晃动。干净、中性且稳定 —— 非常适合用于对话场景或极简主义风格的画面。</p>\n  <section>\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/cf64f494-99f4-4086-d8ed-52016e515c00/public\" data-ratio=\"0.57\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"600\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"329\" data-imgfileid=\"100044649\" data-original-style=\"width: 100%;\" data-index=\"22\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/5e890cdc-8b50-4e30-a24b-8d6847b8574b/640.gif\" data-order=\"15\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"13\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 700%;\">\n  </section>\n  <p>Higgsfield AI 仅需一张照片就能轻松实现百万级运镜，这种「平民化」的创作方式，正在重新定义视频生产的门槛与可能性。</p>\n  <p>面对这场视觉革命，传统广告与影视行业不得不重新思考：当一个人在家就能制作出与专业团队相媲美的作品，创作的价值将何去何从？或许答案不在于技术本身，而在于创意的独特性与表达的深度 —— 这些，才是 AI 尚难以复制的人类才智。</p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">工具链接：</p>\n  <p><span data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">Higgsfield AI ：</span>https://higgsfield.ai/</p>\n  <section data-immersive-translate-walked=\"4d382231-b98e-4570-bcea-526c44b96c5c\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <span data-immersive-translate-walked=\"4d382231-b98e-4570-bcea-526c44b96c5c\"><span data-immersive-translate-walked=\"4d382231-b98e-4570-bcea-526c44b96c5c\">以后我们会带来更多好玩有用的 AI 用例，也欢迎大家进群交流。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section data-immersive-translate-walked=\"4d382231-b98e-4570-bcea-526c44b96c5c\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/f45250c8-d406-4957-fcdf-0a4921873500/public\" alt=\"图片\" data-ratio=\"1.0010649627263046\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"939\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100044594\" data-original-style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;vertical-align: bottom;height: auto !important;visibility: visible !important;width: 677px !important;\" data-index=\"23\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/b743f658-1e4f-46c9-954f-fdadaad904fc/640.png\" data-report-img-idx=\"7\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 700%;\">\n  </section>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "Higgsfield AI 仅需一张照片即可实现电影级运镜效果，大幅降低视频制作门槛，重塑视频创作的可能性。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "Higgsfield AI 仅需一张照片即可实现电影级运镜效果，大幅降低视频制作门槛，重塑视频创作的可能性。",
  "summary": "文章介绍了 Higgsfield AI 这款 AI 视频生成工具，它通过预设运镜模板和高度自定义功能，仅用一张照片就能生成具有复杂摄像机运动效果的视频，实现电影级的动态视频效果。 Higgsfield AI 提供了超过 70 种预设运镜模板，包括 360 度环绕拍摄、子弹时间、机械臂运镜等，并且支持 Mix 混合运镜功能，实现多种镜头动态组合，突破传统物理限制，实现现实中无法完成的镜头语言。 Higgsfield AI 还支持 AI 提示词增强工具，并可与 GPT-4o 等图像生成工具结合，提升视频生成质量。文章通过实际案例展示了 Higgsfield AI 的强大功能和易用性，认为这种“平民化”的创作方式，正在重新定义视频生产的门槛与可能性。面对 AI 技术降低视频制作门槛的趋势，创作者应更注重创意和内容深度。",
